title: ♈️ Aries: They're regretful about pasts conflicts & looking forward to creating more loving moments!
author: Readings by Marvelous Madame Tarot
comment: Yes this resonated to the core!! He is an Aries sun and Taurus moon and I am a Taurus sun and an Aries moon. We both love each other passionately. We have had a back and forth for 4 years on and off. I believe and now he believes that we are twin flames 🔥❤️. Every time we get back together we both level up.
